OL,6,FA postmortem on Stiles' brain found he
OL,7,Fhad chronic traumatic encephalopathy
OL,8,F(CTE), a progressive neurodegenerative
OL,9,Fdisease associated with repetitive
OL,10,Fhead impacts.
OL,12,FStiles' son John is the leader of the
OL,13,FFootball Families for Justice (FFJ)
OL,14,Fgroup which is bringing its campaign
OL,15,Fto Westminster on Tuesday 29 April.
