OL,3,CNew independent regulator 'must tackle
OL,4,Cissue of dementia in football'
OL,6,FFFJ has the support of Greater
OL,7,FManchester Mayor Andy Burnham, and is
OL,8,Fseeking an amendment to the Football
OL,9,FGovernance Bill to give the regulator
OL,10,Fpowers to impose a statutory duty on
OL,11,Fthe football authorities to develop a
OL,12,Fcomprehensive dementia strategy.
OL,14,FChris Evans, the Labour MP for
OL,15,FCaerphilly, said during the second
OL,16,Freading of the Bill in Parliament on
OL,17,FMonday, 28 April: "Footballers suffer
OL,18,Fneurodegenerative diseases at four to
OL,19,Ffive times the national average.
