OL,3,CNew independent regulator 'must tackle
OL,4,Cissue of dementia in football'
OL,6,F"It is something that needs to be
OL,7,Finvestigated.
OL,9,F"When the football regulator comes
OL,10,Fabout, I hope research into medical
OL,11,Fconditions is part of its remit, to
OL,12,Fsupport people who have given so many
OL,13,Fothers so much pleasure over the years.
OL,15,F"I hope that there is something we can
OL,16,Fdo to ensure that the tragedies
OL,17,Fsuffered by Nobby Stiles, Jackie
OL,18,FCharlton and Bobby Charlton ` legends
OL,19,Fwhose names trip off the tongue ` are
OL,20,Fnot suffered by their successors, such
OL,21,Fas Harry Kane."
