OL,6,FTim Farron, the Liberal Democrat MP
OL,7,Ffor Westmorland and Lonsdale, said he
OL,8,Ffelt the Premier League and the
OL,9,FFootball Association "do not do
OL,10,Fjustice" by the families of affected
OL,11,Fformer players.
OL,13,F"Those organisations are meant to help
OL,14,Ffamilies with the care costs of such
OL,15,Fformer professionals, but they do not
OL,16,Fdo so," he said.
