OL,3,CNew independent regulator 'must tackle
OL,4,Cissue of dementia in football'
OL,6,F"Will the Secretary of State meet
OL,7,FFootball Families for Justice so that
OL,8,Fwe can put something in the Bill that
OL,9,Fwill force the wealthy people in
OL,10,Ffootball to support those who suffer?"
OL,12,FCulture Secretary Lisa Nandy responded
OL,13,Fto say she planned to meet with the
OL,14,Ffamilies "shortly".
OL,16,FThe campaign has the backing of
OL,17,Fanother 1966 World Cup winner, Sir
OL,18,FGeoff Hurst, along with former England
OL,19,Fcaptain David Beckham.
