OL,6,FThe FA and the Professional
OL,7,FFootballers' Association (PFA) co-
OL,8,Ffunded arguably the single most
OL,9,Fimportant piece of research which
OL,10,Finforms the debate on dementia in
OL,11,Ffootball, the 2019 FIELD Study, which
OL,12,Ffound footballers were three and a
OL,13,Fhalf times more likely to die of
OL,14,Fneurodegenerative disease than age-
OL,15,Fmatched members of the general
OL,16,Fpopulation.
